{"tid":924801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無對手下連任","createTime":"2018-12-02T11:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T11:23:26.000Z","uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f21545151289e6fbe6aada3ef2b8308c5eb4aee","tid":924801,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】民主黨今日改選領導層。<br />\n<br />\n兩年一度的改選包括選出新任正副主席、中央委員會及紀律委員會等成員，預料現任主席胡志偉 、副主席羅健熙會在無競爭下順利連任。立法會議員尹兆堅參選另一個副主席席位，預料亦會無競爭下當選。<br />\n<br />\n中委會委員方面，據了解民主黨早前收到29份參選表格，競爭沒往年激烈。其中民主黨元老張文光以及楊森都放棄角逐連任，另外前主席劉慧卿 則報名參選紀律委員會。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=329296&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D329296%26refer%3D&d=iUjNIk4lcABczLB7tWF%2FOQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0976fd96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D329296%26refer%3D&h=96b7da1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=329296&amp;refer=</a>"}]}